      "rationale": "A systematic mesh convergence study was conducted across three refinement levels. Construct stiffness QoI changed by 1.4% between medium and fine mesh; yield force changed by 1.1%. Grid Convergence Index (GCI) computed per Roache methodology; GCI_fine < 1.8% for all QoIs. Discretization error contribution to total simulation uncertainty quantified and included in E/uval calculation."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical solver error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
