      "rationale": "Nonlinear static analysis employed Newton-Raphson iteration with adaptive load stepping. Force equilibrium residuals monitored at each substep and confirmed below 1e-5. No unconverged substeps recorded. Numerical solver error estimated as negligible relative to discretization and model-form uncertainties."
