      "rationale": "Validation activities used production-equivalent non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested under the identical ASTM F1717 fixture configuration and loading protocol as specified in the COU. No surrogate geometries or substitute materials were employed. The validation domain closely matches the intended use domain; the sole gap (single test condition vs. COU's broader environmental envelope) is captured in the Test conditions factor above."
