    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required level for a Medium model risk, Medium assurance level assessment. The single deficient factor (Test conditions, achieved level 2 vs. required level 3) is accepted based on the quasi-static nature of the loading, corroborating published literature, and the conservative acceptance bounds applied to the output comparison. All three QoIs satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and MAPE < 10%. The FEA modeling framework is accepted as adequately credible for the stated COU.",
